<p>
  <span class="nym">Sophia</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Greek</span> <i>σοφία</i> 'wisdom'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 2nd C martyr, a 4th C martyr, a 15th C queen of Bohemia, and a 15th-16th C grand duchess of Moscow.</p>
</div>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>The name is sometimes, incorrectly, identified with <span class="lang">Arabic</span> <i>Sāfiya</i>, but that is an unrelated name, identical with the Arabic word 'to be pure'.</p>
  
  


